-	7 sources observe the performance gain of 1%~10.13% at CSI feedback overhead B (medium overhead);
-	8 sources observe the performance gain of 0.85%~8% at CSI feedback overhead C (large overhead);
-	Note: 4 sources observe gain of 0% and 5.6%~5.7% at RU≤39%, 4.2%~5.8%  at RU 40%-69%, 23%~50% at RU≥70%, which bias from the majority ranges.
